        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-18-21-19-39-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:84e1106395014eb20dd5f3258482b7bde0ab5a9b725d53e02813466fd1160634a5f1210bbfe0c3668117daf3c48a2c88050371151ec32b70b90e81d9a1abc3c4"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/04/2026-04-18-21-19-39-mozilla-central/firefox-151.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
